body:
Version of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/24617 plus https://github.com/cms-data/L1Trigger-L1TMuon/pull/16 that does not require changes to cms-data, which cannot be deployed in Online DQM.  Temporary placement of 6 small text files in L1Trigger/L1TMuonEndCap directory for use in data-emulator comparisons in Online DQM.

Best regards,
Andrew
title: EMTF new LCT coordinate conversion LUTs for DQM
